name: Amzncoin
description: Amazon coin is a new virtual currency, which can be used by users all over the world to buy Amazon applications, games and props in applications. In the future, Amazon will provide tens of millions of dollars of Amazon coins for users to try, and buy applications, games and props in the app for free on Amazon Mall. And in the future, you can use Amazon coins to pay for any product owned by Amazon. AMZNcoin is committed to creating a better web3.0 era and making payment and life easier.
